videos.headline: Bobcat turnover gives the Eagles a chance to score
videos.description: Ohio's WR Brendan Cope fumble is recovered by Eastern Michigan's Brody Hoying late in the second quarter and would result in a field goal.

videos.headline: Bobcat's score 1st TD of game in final seconds of the 2nd quarter.
videos.description: Eagle's QB Brogan Roback's pass is intercepted by Bobcat's CB Bradd Ellis for a 46-yard return for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Eastern Michigan QB Roback delivers big for 1st down.
videos.description: QB Brogan Roback delivers a 25-yard pass to WR Antoine Porter for a Eagle's first down.

videos.headline: Eagles' trick play leads to 1st down
videos.description: Eastern Michigan's QB Brogan Roback throws to WR Isaac Holder who passes to WR John Niupalau for 34 yards for the first down.

videos.headline: Eagles' QB Roback connects to Bailey for TD in 1st OT
videos.description: Brogan Roback throws high 25-yard pass to WR Sergio Bailey II for the touchdown in overtime.

videos.headline: Ohio QB Rourke pass to Coupe for TD ties game
videos.description: QB Nathan Rourke delivers to WR Brendan Cope for 8 yards to tie game in overtime.

videos.headline: Bobcats' WR Odom gets winning TD in OT
videos.description: Ohio QB Nathan Rourke throws seven yards to freshman WR Cameron Odom for a touchdown in the Bobcats' 27-20 overtime win.
